Ranger Help for: assess
=======================

SYNTAX:      assess <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain.
SLOT COST:   2
BASE SP:     10

SUMMARY:
Evaluate a target creature, sizing up its strength, weapons, and
defenses. Information revealed depends on your guild level: higher
ranked Rangers glean more detail. This is a prerequisite for the
calm and strike skill branches.

=============================================================================
